  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Catalog Description</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">The CSCE 670 catalog description covers representation, storage, access to multimedia document collections, fundamental data structures and algorithms, and techniques to design and evaluate retrieval systems including indexing, compressing, and querying.</data>
