<node id="CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: Web Search Concepts">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: Web Search Concepts</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 670, learners will be able to define and explain key concepts and models relevant to web search, such as text indexing, retrieval models, evaluation, Web crawling, PageRank, and learning to rank.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774749730</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: Recommender Systems Concepts">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: Recommender Systems Concepts</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 670, learners will be able to define and explain key concepts and models relevant to recommender systems, including collaborative filtering, matrix factorization, evaluation, and implicit recommendation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774749730</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: System Design and Evaluation">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: System Design and Evaluation</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 670, learners will be able to design, implement, and evaluate the core algorithms underlying functional web search and recommendation systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774749730</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: Research Application">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Learning Outcome: Research Application</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 670, learners will be able to identify salient features and apply recent research results in web search and recommender systems, including adversarial information retrieval.</data>
